node.text: As an Ambassador for @womenforwomenuk I am proudly supporting their #VirtualCarBoot Sale, taking place this Saturday. Designers and fashion icons are emptying their wardrobes to donate items to raise money for women survivors of war. I will be joining them to sell three items too - visit @womenforwomenuk to find out more and go there at 11am (BST) this Saturday to shop for a good cause!
